        <h2>Dairy Management</h2>
        <p>Unlike other careers, the management of a dairy business is rather different. It is done at a micro level and the dairy farmer usually sets his/her own goals, provides the management of the business and performs a part of the labour, as well. This, as a result, makes diary management a rather tricky job, as it is often difficult to separate management from labor.</p>
        
