        <p>The  dairy industry is fraught with many difficulties such as inefficiency, deterioration of perishable food items, unsatisfactory quality of commodities, malpractices in weights and measures, mismatch of demand and supply, long waiting times, exorbitant corruption, rude behavior of shopkeepers and poor service delivery. Streamlining of SCM processes will result in increased operational efficiency, thereby reducing transit losses and pilferages.   </p>
        
